<area shape="rect" id="node17" title="dsgrid.config.project_config.ProjectConfigModel

Represents project configurations

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;project_id (str): A unique project identifier that is project&#45;specific (e.g., &#39;standard&#45;scenarios&#45;2021&#39;).
 &#160;&#160;&#160;version (Optional[str]): Version, generated by dsgrid. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;name (str): A project name to accompany the ID.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;description (str): Detailed project description.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;status (ProjectRegistryStatus(DSGEnum)): project registry status. Default is ProjectRegistryStatus.INITIAL_REGISTRATION.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;datasets (List[InputDatasetModel]): List of input datasets for the project.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;dimensions (DimensionsModel): List of `base` and `supplemental` dimensions.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;dimension_mappings (DimensionMappingsModel): List of project mappings. Initialized with base&#45;to&#45;base and base&#45;to&#45;supplemental mappings. dataset&#45;to&#45;project mappings are added by dsgrid as datasets get registered with the project. Default is base_to_supplemental_references=[] dataset_to_project={}.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;id (Optional[str]): Registry database ID. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;key (Optional[str]): Registry database key. Default is None.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;rev (Optional[str]): Registry database revision. Default is None.
" alt="" coords="5,2459,548,2795"/>
